         <abstract id="aspace_ff7cc91eecd7ebd4ad1a5fbe1a0c69e2">Chiefly memoranda, outlines, notes, bibliographies, newspaper clippings, and other materials relating to the courses in bibliography that Keogh taught at Yale University from 1924 to 1938. There is also a small amount of personal correspondence, 1898-1916.</abstract>
